OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAn overcast start with periods
OL,6,Fof rain, heavy at times and combining
OL,7,Fwith gales to bring decidedly un-
OL,8,FSpring like weather. Clearing to
OL,9,Fblustery showers during the morning,
OL,10,Fwith these heavy for the afternoon
OL,11,Fbringing the risk of hail and thunder.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FStrong to gale southwest
OL,14,Fwinds pushing showers across the
OL,15,FNorthern Isles, occasional for the
OL,16,Fevening, turning more frequent and
OL,17,Fheavy overnight, with some fleeting
OL,18,Fsleet and snow possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
