OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FFrequent showers continuing,
OL,6,Fwhich turn heavy at times bringing the
OL,7,Frisk of hail and thunder. Strong west
OL,8,Fto southwest winds perhaps touching
OL,9,Fgale force at first.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,12,FScattered showers for Saturday mixed
OL,13,Fwith limited brighter spells. Showers
OL,14,Fand longer periods of rain for Sunday,
OL,15,Fcombining with strong to gale winds.
OL,16,FOnly scattered light showers for
OL,17,FMonday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
